    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <head type="title"><app>
                    <lem wit="#KK #M">Index XVII.</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P">Index VIII.</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#B">Index decimusseptimus</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R">Index XVI.</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2">Index XVII., in quo regnum Ladislai quarti describitur</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S1 #S2 #S3">Index XVI. de Ladislao rege a Comanis caeso</rdg>
                    </app></head>
                <p>
                <s n="1">﻿Ei successit Ladislaus filius regnavitque annos XVI.</s>
                <s n="2"><app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">Fudit et</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#M">Fudit</rdg>
                    </app> is Bohemorum copias <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B">Octocaro</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #M">Ottocaro</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">Othocaro</rdg>
                    </app> eorum rege in Moravia caeso, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">fudit et</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#M">fudit</rdg>
                    </app> et exercitum Comanorum, qui <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L1 #L2">(duce Oldamuro)</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">duce Oldamuro</rdg>
                    </app> invasit Hungariam, ut <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">eam</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L2">illam</rdg>
                    </app> illius ditioni <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3"><sic>subigerent</sic></lem>
                        <rdg wit="#M">subigeret</rdg>
                    </app>.<note type="critic" corresp="RKK">1–2 = Th 2.78.</note></s>
                <s n="3">Sub hoc rege Tartari infestis armis denuo Hungariam ingressi sunt, qui
                    omnia <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #S1 #S2">paene</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S3 #M">pene</rdg>
                    </app> longe lateque <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B">usque</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">usque<add type="insert"> ad</add></rdg>
                    </app> Pestum direptionibus atque incendiis <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R">absumpserunt</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">absumserunt</rdg>
                    </app>, anno deinde ab eorum ingressu secundo non sine <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">maxima</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L2">magna</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">praeda</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">preda</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">excessere</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">excaessere</rdg>
                    </app>.</s>
                <s n="4">Duxerat hic rex uxorem filiam Caroli <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">secundi</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#R">II.</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Siciliae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">Sicilie</rdg>
                    </app> regis, ex qua plures suscepit filios, sed ipse uxore liberisque despectis
                    cum Comanis mulieribus <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B">(licet essent a Christiana religione alienae)</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">licet essent a Christiana religione
                            alienae</rdg>
                    </app> omnem suam vitam libidinose vivendo <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R">consumpsit</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">consumsit</rdg>
                    </app>, quin ea de causa regni sui curas omnes <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #S1 #S2">paene</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S3 #M">pene</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">praetermisit</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">pretermisit</rdg>
                    </app> ita, ut non modo sui omnisque <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B">regii</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">regni</rdg>
                    </app> decoris sed suae quoque <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">religionis</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z">reigionis</rdg>
                    </app> penitus oblitus esse videretur.</s>
                <s n="5">Quae res causam praebuit suis popularibus, ut ipsum non mediocri odio <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">prosequerentur</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L1">prosequaerentur</rdg>
                    </app>.<note type="critic" corresp="RKK">3–5 = Th 2.79. – 4 ex qua plures
                        suscepit filios: ceteri scriptores horum filiorum nullam mentionem faciunt,
                        cf. Mór Wertner: <title>Az Árpádok családi története</title>. Nagybecskerek
                        1892. 536.</note></s>
                <s n="6">Percrebuit tanti <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P">flagicii</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">flagitii</rdg>
                    </app> rumor apud sacrosanctae Romanae <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">ecclesiae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">ecclesie</rdg>
                    </app> senatum, nec non apud <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">plerosque</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">plaerosque</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #R #L2 #S1 #S2">saeculares</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #L1 #S3 #M">seculares</rdg>
                    </app> catholicos principes, qui <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">infamem</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">infamen</rdg>
                    </app> eius vitam <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L2">(<app>
                                <lem wit="#KK #P #B">uti</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#L2">ut</rdg>
                            </app> par erat)</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">uti par erat</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B">abhominabantur</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">abominabantur</rdg>
                    </app>.</s>
                <s n="7">Itaque missus est unus e numero cardinalium ab apostolica sede legatus, qui
                    re cognita, si rex perseverare vellet in scelere, in ipsum sententiam ferret
                    anathematis privationisque regni iudicio ipsum <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">condemnaret</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">condempnaret</rdg>
                    </app>, quod a legato post inquisitionem quam diligentissimam effectum est.</s>
                <s n="8">Idque fieri petiere cuncti regni viri primarii, quandoquidem sceleratus rex
                    maluit <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">noxiae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L2">noxie</rdg>
                    </app> indulgere libidini quam et abstinere flagitio et maximo parere
                    pontifici.</s>
                <s n="9"><app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Ceterum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2">Caeterum</rdg>
                    </app> ultor scelerum deus non est passus, ut impius homo ea execranda facinora
                    impune perpetraret diutius, haud enim multo post, quam legatus rediit ad urbem
                    Romam, a Comanis, quibus maxime fidebat, ob morum asperitatem <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">necatus est</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P">necatus est<del><add type="insert"> ab</add></del><note
                                type="critic">P addit et del.</note></rdg>
                    </app> anno ab incarnato filio dei <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #R #S1 #S2 #S3">M-o</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #L1 #L2 #M">millesimo</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L2">CCLXXXX-o</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #M">ducentesimo nonagesimo</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L1">CCLXXXX.</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#R #S1 #S2 #S3">CCXC.</rdg>
                    </app>.<note type="critic" corresp="RKK">6–9 = Th 2.80. – In fine: <hi
                            rend="italic">a Comanis... M-o CCLXXXX-o</hi> = Th 2.81.</note></s>
            </p>
            </div>
